After the game, Lang Ping also pointed out in an interview: "Third game, because of the mistake we sent about 8 points."
Of course, the strength of the Dutch women's volleyball team should not be underestimated, China's women's volleyball before the preparation of difficult, although lost a game, but everything is still in the hands of Lang Ping, "and the strong team to win and lose is very normal, play five games is also very normal, so we said to the players to focus," Lang Ping said.
In the fourth game, the players actively adjusted their status, Zhang Changning opened in the offensive end of the fire, and the single game scored 8 points, making great achievements for the team to win.
Since the game, 11 rounds of confrontation is currently only two rounds, although the Chinese women's volleyball team has touched the championship trophy with one hand, but in the game against the Netherlands team did sound the alarm to the Chinese women's volleyball team: the more critical moments, the more to go all out.
In another game on the 27th, the Russian and American women's volleyball team played 5 sets, and the United States failed to take all three points from the opponent, so that the Chinese women's volleyball team could defend the line as long as it took three points in the game against Serbia.
All these situations are moving towards a favorable situation for the Chinese women's volleyball team.
However, although the Serbian team's six main players are all absent, this does not mean that they will easily give three points to the Chinese team.
From the current form of the standings, the Serbian team has basically missed the medal, which means that they can be in the game against the Chinese women's volleyball team "lightly loaded", put down the burden to hit the opponent, and the Chinese team is burdened with the pressure to win the championship, the state may appear ups and downs.
In addition, the replacement of the Serbian team is not "manned" lamb, before the battle with the Dutch team, the two sides fought 5 games, Serbia's second team finally 3:2 reversed the Netherlands' all-force lineup, which shows the depth of its lineup.
Before the third stage of the game, Lang Ping also said that the Dutch and Sai teams are not good to deal with: "Osaka's game will be very difficult, we still have to be as usual, seriously prepare."
Now the defending trumpet has been sounded, the game has really entered the "white heat stage."
On the strength of the lineup, the Chinese women's volleyball team is above the opponent, but the last critical moment, but also depends on whether the women's volleyball girls can play the normal level, in the field to release themselves.
The University of Macau held the "2nd Macao Stem Cell Seminar" today (27), attracting more than 100 experts and scholars from the United States, Singapore, the Mainland, Hong Kong and Macao, who are engaged in "external stem cell" research, and sharing and discussing the latest technology and development of stem cell research with teachers and students of Macao universities.
Vice-Chancellor of the University of Australia (Research) Ge Wei said that stem cell research has medical value and is also one of the key scientific research projects of the University of Australia, and this seminar will help promote Macao's research and development in the field of stem cells.
Ge Wei said that as a leading international comprehensive university on the west coast of the Guangdong-Hong Kong-Macao Greater Bay Area, the University is committed to building a talent training base and scientific and technological innovation center on the West Bank of the Greater Bay Area to help the innovation and development of the Bay Area.
The seminar brought together research experts from stem cells at home and abroad to share the latest technologies, which will help promote the research and development of stem cells in Macao.
Deng Xia, dean of the University's School of Health Sciences, said that in recent years, the University has continuously strengthened scientific research and innovation and transformation, and has also significantly improved the number and quality of papers, and the University has also achieved fruitful results in stem cell research.
At the meeting, a group of well-known scholars shared cutting-edge knowledge of stem cell research and cutting-edge technology.
Academician of the Chinese Academy of Sciences and Dean of the School of Spiritual Translational Medicine of Kunming University of Science and Technology in Yunnan, Ji Weizhi, explained the use of 3D culture system to study the process of monkeys and human embryos in vitro and its molecular mechanisms; Jing Naihe, a researcher at the Shanghai Institute of Biochemical Cells of the Chinese Academy of Sciences, explained the decision and organization of space-time changes in the cell lineage of mouse embryos after implantation from a single-cell and molecular level; Wang Yong, a professor at Pennsylvania State University, showed you how to use bio-based hydrogel to simulate the micronest of stem cells for survival and transportation.
Xu Renhe, Vice President (Research) of the College of Health Sciences of the University of Australia, Chen Guokai, Assistant Dean, and Wang Chunming, Associate Professor of the University of Australia China Medical Research Institute, also introduced their latest important results.
The "2nd Macao Stem Cell Seminar" was organized by the School of Health Sciences of the University of Macau, co-organized by the Chinese Medical Research Institute of the University of Macau and the State Key Laboratory of Chinese Quality Research of the University of Macao, and participated in the meeting by Chen Yi'an, Acting Senior Manager of the Macao Science and Technology Development Fund.
The seminar has a total of 11 academic reports, including embryo development and tissue generation, translational medicine, stem cell mechanism research and application, biological materials and applications.
The atmosphere at the seminar was warm, and the participants actively discussed and shared the latest research and views on relevant technologies.
Xu Renhe said that the seminar provided a platform for stem cell experts in the Greater Bay Area and other regions to exchange and cooperate, and also provided valuable learning opportunities for students.
The awarding ceremony of the National Medal and the National Honor Award Ceremony of the People's Republic of China will be held solemnly.
With the approval of the Central Committee of the Communist Party of China, the awarding ceremony of the National Medal and the National Honor Award Ceremony will be held in the Great Hall of the People at 10 a.m. on September 29.
General Secretary of the CPC Central Committee, President Xi Jinping, Chairman of the Central Military Commission, will award the "Order of the Republic" and the National Medal of Friendship and the State Medal of Honor and deliver important speeches to the recipients of the National Medal and the National Medal of Honor.
With the approval of the Central Committee of the Communist Party of China, the awarding ceremony of the National Medal and the National Honor Award Ceremony will be held at the Great Hall of the People in Beijing at 10 a.m. on September 29.
This is the "Order of the Republic".
The "Order of the Republic" is based on red and gold, and the chapter body adopts the elements of the national emblem, five-pointed star, Yellow River, Yangtze River, peaks, peony, etc. The chapter chain adopts elements such as Chinese knots, such as ruyi, orchids, and the overall use of cold-press molding, flower silk inlaid, enamel and other craftsmanship, symbolizing the great contribution made by the recipients of the medal to the construction and development of the Republic.
This is the "Friendship Medal".
The "Friendship Medal" is based on gold and blue, and the chapter body adopts elements such as peace doves, earth, handshake, lotus flowers, etc. The chapter chain adopts elements such as Chinese knots, ten thousand young, peony, jade, orchid grass, and the whole use of traditional crafts such as flower silk inlaid and enamel is handmade, symbolizing the friendship and unity of the Chinese people and the people of all countries, and wishing all countries in the world to prosper and develop together.
This is the National Medal of Honor.
The national honorary title medal is based on red and gold, the chapter body adopts five-star, Tiananmen, peony, flag, light and other elements, the chapter chain adopts elements such as Chinese knots, flowers, and the overall use of cold pressure molding, flower mosaic, enamel and other craftsmanship, symbolizing the major contribution made by the recipient of the national honorary title in various fields in various industries, highlighting the demonstration and leading role, inspiring the people of all ethnic groups in the country to not forget their original intention, keep in mind the mission, and make the Chinese dream of the great rejuvenation of the Chinese nation.
The Central Radio and Television Station and Xinhua Network will broadcast the award ceremony live, and the key central news websites such as the People's Network, CCTV Network, and China Network, as well as the People's Daily client, Xinhua News Agency client, CCTV news client, and other new media platforms will be broadcast simultaneously.
