In order to better meet the sustainable development needs of Vietnam’s aviation industry.
Research shows that manufacturing has become the focus of attention of major countries in the world - Xinhua
Xinhua News Agency, Hefei, September 27, a few days ago, the national intellectual property operation public service platform in Hefei, Anhui Province released the "Global Manufacturing Innovation Index White Paper".
The white paper shows that the manufacturing industry has become the focus of attention of major countries around the world.
This is what the reporter learned at the "Intellectual Property Operation and Protection Forum of the 2019 World Manufacturing Conference" held in Hefei.
The forum focused on intellectual property rights to help China's manufacturing upgrade, from the macro level of policy interpretation and the micro-perspective of enterprise practice, comprehensively explored innovative measures for the operation and protection of intellectual property rights in the manufacturing field, in-depth discussion of hot topics of intellectual property protection in the manufacturing industry, continuously improved the ability to use intellectual property rights, and accelerated the construction of intelligent upgrading advantages of manufacturing.
The forum invited scholars from the State Intellectual Property Office, the Chinese Academy of Sciences, and experts from relevant domestic and foreign industry organizations and professional research institutions to share experiences and suggestions on how to strengthen intellectual property protection and promote the use of intellectual property rights.
At the forum, the Anhui Provincial Market Supervision and Administration Bureau issued the "Patent Navigation Anhui Province Innovation and Development Quality Analysis Evaluation" report, according to the calculation results of the patent navigation regional innovation high-quality development index, Anhui Province's 2018 patent navigation regional innovation and high-quality development index ranked eighth among the 31 provinces and cities in the country, and the innovation factor agglomeration index ranked fourth in the country.
The forum was hosted by the People's Government of Anhui Province, and was jointly hosted by the Anhui Provincial Market Supervision Administration Bureau, the National Intellectual Property Operation Public Service Platform and the China Intellectual Property Development Alliance.
