Wuhan promotes the intelligent transformation of industrial enterprises and gives up to 20 million yuan in subsidies
The reporter learned from the city series of "Celebrating New China Welcome Military Games" held by the Wuhan Municipal Government Press Office on the 27th that since this year, the city has accelerated the transformation of industrial intelligence and implemented transformation subsidies of up to 20 million yuan.
Up to now, more than 800 industrial enterprises above the scale of intelligent transformation needs information.
Zhang Hong, deputy director of Wuhan Economic and Information Bureau, introduced that since this year, Wuhan has launched an action plan for the intelligent transformation of industrial enterprises, providing free consulting and diagnostic services for industrial enterprises above the scale of demand and proposing solutions, and comprehensively promoting a new round of high-level enterprise technological transformation.
According to the plan, Wuhan City publicly selects a number of professional diagnostic service institutions every year, and carries out an intelligent transformation demand survey for all industrial enterprises above scale in the city through the opening of columns, questionnaires, door-to-door filling and other forms.
Up to now, more than 800 regulatory industrial enterprises have collected information on the demand for intelligent transformation of industrial enterprises, accounting for nearly one-third of the number of industrial enterprises above the city's scale.
Five municipal diagnostic platforms have organized teams to enter the enterprise in batches to carry out "one-to-one" on-site assessment and program demonstration.
Zhang Hong introduced that at present, the city is organizing the implementation of 373 intelligent transformation projects, with a total planned investment of 29.76 billion yuan, Hongxin Communication Huazhong's first 5G intelligent production line, Motorola's national leading intelligent mobile phone production line, Wuhan Siemens transformer digital unmanned factory, aerospace science and technology industry's first batch satellite production line, Huisheng biological world's leading new veterinary drug intelligent production line, Oubang smart home Internet of Things intelligent production line and a number of leading intelligent workshops and smart factories in the industry have started construction.
