Whether from the level of enterprise competition, consumer experience, or from the regional aviation integration, Beijing-Tianjin-Hebei development integration level, have far-reaching impact and positive significance.
On September 25, Beijing Daxing International Airport was officially opened.
The Beijing News reporter learned from the Beijing Municipal Development and Reform Commission that the capital airport is already in a supersaturated operation state, and the opening of Daxing International Airport will enhance the air service capacity of the capital.
After Shanghai, Beijing has become the second city with two airports in China, and Shanghai Hongqiao International Airport mainly serves domestic aviation affairs, Pudong Airport is similar to international shipping aviation, and the future Capital Airport and Daxing Airport will also serve the differentiated positioning of different domestic and international aviation services to provide more segmented services.
From the perspective of business development, the opening of Daxing Airport is more positive for the capital airport.
Capital Airport in 2018 passenger throughput exceeded 100 million people, ranking first in the country, but compared with the rapid growth of business demand, there is still a significant poor capacity, especially the international route demand has a large gap.
In order to better serve the needs of domestic and foreign passenger travel, business travel and so on, to adapt to Beijing's increasingly open, international-in-line urban development trend, Daxing International Airport is positioned as a large international hub airport, plans to meet the annual passenger throughput of 100 million people, cargo and mail throughput of 4 million tons in the future.
Therefore, the two airports do not have overlapping positioning, and they also have enough market space for different customer groups.
From the perspective of economic accounting, the navigation of Daxing International Airport will obviously form a win-win effect, alleviate the tension in Beijing's air capacity, accelerate the growth rate of passenger and cargo throughput, and create an incremental cake for the dual-core operation of the capital aviation.
From the user's point of view, with the opening of Daxing International Airport, the future does not have to be concentrated in the capital airport travel, but also to reduce the route too concentrated caused by a series of problems, such as the station security time, passenger boarding speed is slow, indirectly increase the aircraft and passengers in the airport detention time, increase the burden of airport operation, through the capital airport shipping burden, in fact, also improve the passenger travel experience.
According to the media's calculation of the time and cost of various transportation routes to large international airports, such as starting from the South Fifth Ring Road, the Beijing Kai Expressway directly to the Daxing Airport Expressway, driving 50 minutes can be reached, the oil money is about 40 yuan, and the high-speed fee is 15 yuan; while the choice of the rail transit subway Daxing Airport Line, the distance is limited to 20 kilometers and 30 kilometers, the fare is divided into 10 yuan, 25 yuan, 35 yuan three tranches; the public can also take the Jingxiong Intercity, from Beijing West Station to Daxing Airport Station.
In general, the public to Daxing Airport has a variety of means of transport to choose from, and the cost and time are also within a more reasonable range.
From the perspective of trend development: Daxing Airport is positioned as the Beijing-Tianjin-Hebei transportation hub, so it is a little farther from the Beijing District, but it has strengthened the radiation to Hebei and Tianjin, which has facilitated more people's travel, which is of great significance to the economic development of Hebei and Tianjin.
In the future, Hebei and Tianjin passengers can enjoy more international air route services provided by Daxing International Airport, which can be seen from the traffic planning of Daxing Airport.
The supporting transportation facilities of Daxing Airport are very perfect, in addition to the new airport line directly to Daxing Airport in Beijing, there are also a number of highways connecting Daxing Airport and surrounding areas.
Just as passengers from Dongguan, Foshan, Qingyuan and other cities in Guangdong can go to Guangzhou Baiyun Airport through highways such as Guangfo and Guangshen, residents of Langfang and Xiong'an New Area around Beijing will also benefit from Daxing Airport and obtain convenient and efficient air services.
It can be seen that the navigation of Daxing International Airport not only adds a few runways and several aircraft, whether it is from the level of enterprise competition, consumer experience, or from the regional aviation integration, Beijing-Tianjin-Hebei development integration, have far-reaching impact and positive significance, not only related to the long-term layout and development of Beijing's shipping industry, but also to provide diversified choices for the travel of the majority of residents of Beijing-Tianjin-Hebei, promote the further improvement of the quality of service in Beijing's shipping industry.
