State Council Information Office Releases White Paper on China and the World in the New Era
On the occasion of the 70th anniversary of the founding of the People's Republic of China, the Information Office of the State Council released a white paper on "China and the World in
Xu Lin, vice minister of the Central Propaganda Department and director of the State Council Information Office, said that the white paper systematically introduced China's development achievements, development path and development trend, and elaborated on China's relationship with the world, so as to enhance the international community's understanding and understanding of China's development.
The white paper pointed out that in the past 70 years, under the leadership of the Communist Party of China, China has undergone tremendous changes, creating a miracle of development unprecedented in human history, especially since the 18th National Congress of the Communist Party of China, China's development has made historic achievements and undergone historic changes.
Through a large amount of data and facts, the white paper introduces the great achievements, significance and world contributions of China's development in the past 70 years.
The white paper pointed out that China has completed the development process of developed countries in decades, and the total economy has jumped to the second place in the world, with nearly 1.4 billion people getting rid of material shortages, generally reaching a well-off level and enjoying unprecedented dignity and rights.
The white paper emphasizes that in the past 70 years, the Chinese people have made a new world from scratch, self-reliant and hard-working; in the past 70 years, China has developed in the interaction with the world, embracing the world, learning from the world, and contributing to the world; in the past 70 years, China has made contributions to world peace while achieving self-development, and has injected impetus into the common development of all countries.
The white paper pointed out that in the past 70 years, the fundamental reason for the success of China's development is that under the leadership of the Communist Party of China, the Chinese people have found the correct development path of socialism with Chinese characteristics and have unswervingly followed this path.
The white paper emphasizes that the path of socialism with Chinese characteristics is a road established from the perspective of its own national conditions, a road that puts the interests of the people first, a road of reform and innovation, a path of common development in opening up, and a path of comprehensive rule of law.
This development path of China, in line with China's national conditions, to adapt to the requirements of the times, will be more and more with the times to show a bright development prospect.
In response to the international community's concern about China's development, the white paper emphasizes that realizing national prosperity, national rejuvenation and people's happiness is both the dream of the Chinese people and the common dream of the people of all countries.
The white paper pointed out that China is the main stabilizer and power source of world economic growth, all-round opening up creates more opportunities for the development of all countries, China provides more public goods for the international community, China's development provides experience and reference for other developing countries, and China will never take the path of "national strength will dominate".
In the face of the question of "what happened to the world and what should mankind do", the white paper pointed out that the world is in a big change that has not been seen in a hundred years, and human society is both full of hope and full of challenges.
China has proposed to build a community with a shared future for mankind, open up a new path of development with win-win cooperation and joint construction and sharing, and provide new choices for human development.
The white paper calls on all countries to unite and build a new type of international relations, promote a new type of economic globalization, safeguard the international system with the United Nations as the core, promote exchanges and mutual learning among civilizations, jointly promote the construction of a community with a shared future for mankind, and build a better world.
With the increasing development of China, the international community is generally concerned about how China is living with the world.
The white paper pointed out that China's development cannot be separated from the world, and the world's peaceful development, prosperity and stability cannot be separated from China.
China has always placed its own development in the coordinate system of human development, adhered to win-win cooperation and common development, adhered to maintaining and promoting economic globalization, actively developed global partnership, firmly supported multilateralism, safeguarded international fairness and justice, promoted the high-quality development of the Belt and Road Initiative, actively participated in leading the reform and construction of the global governance system, and always be a builder of world peace, a contributor to global development, and a defender of the international order.
At present, China's development has entered a new era.
The white paper pointed out that in the new era of China, the determination to take the path of socialism with Chinese characteristics will not change, the determination to learn from each other and win-win cooperation with other countries will not change, and the determination to walk hand in hand with the world will not change.
The white paper concludes by noting that in today's world, the future of all countries has never been more closely linked.
The white paper "China and the World in the New Era" consists of forewords, body papers and concluding remarks, with a full text of more than 29,000 words.
The white paper was released in eight languages, such as China, Britain, France, Russia, Germany, West, Afghanistan, and Japan, and was published by the People's Publishing House and the Foreign Language Publishing House respectively, and was distributed in Xinhua Bookstore across the country.
