Liu Kun, Minister of Finance: 67 central enterprises and financial institutions have transferred 86.01 billion yuan of state-owned capital to enrich the social security fund.
Finance Minister Liu Kun said on the 27th that as of now, 67 central enterprises and central financial institutions have completed the transfer of some state-owned capital to enrich the social security fund, with a total transfer of state-owned capital of about 861 billion yuan.
