"The transfer of some state-owned capital to enrich the social security fund is an important measure to reform and improve the basic pension insurance system, is the development of state-owned enterprises to share the results of the national people and the basic pension insurance system in the generational fairness of the full embodiment, is a based on the current, take into account the long-term policy measures."
In 2017, the State Council issued the "Implementation Plan for the Transfer of Some State-owned Capital to Enrich the Social Security Fund", requiring the selection of some central enterprises and some provinces to carry out pilot projects.
According to Liu Kun, the preliminary work of the transfer has achieved positive results.
At the central level, three batches of 67 central enterprises and central financial institutions have been transferred, and the total capital of the transfer is about 860.1 billion yuan.
Among them, the transfer of central financial institutions by the Ministry of Finance to perform the duties of investors has been basically completed.
The transfer of central enterprises has a certain scale.
At the local level, the pre-relocation work of enterprises has been carried out one after another.
By the end of 2018, the pilot work in Zhejiang and Yunnan provinces was basically completed, transferring 15.8 billion yuan and 18.5 billion yuan of state-owned capital respectively.
In addition to the pilot provinces, other provinces have also successively carried out preliminary preparatory work for the transfer, laying the foundation for the next step of the implementation of the transfer.
According to the joint issuance of the notice by the Ministry of Finance, the Ministry of Human Resources and Social Security, the State-owned Assets Supervision and Administration Commission, and the Securities Regulatory Commission, the central and local governments transferred some state-owned capital to enrich the Social Security Fund in 2019 and was basically completed by the end of 2020.
The meeting held on the same day made a specific deployment for the comprehensive implementation of the transfer work.
The meeting stressed the need to complete the transfer work pragmatically and efficiently.
"According to the schedule, the transfer work should be basically completed by the end of 2020.
The rotation work time is tight, the task is heavy.
Liu Kun said that all regions and departments should carefully organize and carefully arrange to ensure that the transfer work is completed as required; solidly promote the work, accurately grasp the content of the transfer policy; strengthen communication and coordination, and solve difficult problems in a timely manner.
State-owned capital transfer to enrich the social security fund - from the starting point of "enriching the social security fund money bag", the destination is to provide strong support for pension security.
However, the author believes that this is not a simple equity "physical displacement", but opened the "mathematical addition".
On September 20, the Ministry of Finance, the Ministry of Human Resources and Social Security, the State-owned Assets Supervision and Administration Commission, the State Administration of Taxation and the Securities Regulatory Commission jointly issued the "Notice on Comprehensively Pushing and Transferring Some State-owned Capital to Fill the Work of the Social Security Fund", clarifying the timetable for the transfer of state-owned capital to the Social Security Fund, that is, the central and local transfer of some state-owned capital to enrich the work of the Social Security Fund in 2019.
After the publication of the document, the Ministry of Finance and other departments have also implemented it quickly.
On September 25, the Ministry of Finance transferred all 10% of the shares held by the Industrial and Commercial Bank and the Agricultural Bank to the Social Security Fund, and the total value of the two equity transfers exceeded 115 billion yuan.
According to the regulations, the social security foundation and other undertaking entities, as financial investors, enjoy the right to income, disposal and the right to know the transfer of state-owned equity.
The ICBC and the Agricultural Bank said in the announcement that this change in equity will not lead to changes in the controlling shareholders and actual controllers of the Bank.
In this regard, the author believes that the transfer of similar state-owned enterprises is not a simple change in equity ownership, but can stimulate a series of effects of "addition operations".
The first step of some state-owned transfer of social security "addition results" can naturally reflect the ownership of state-owned enterprises by the whole people and the development results shared by the whole people.
After years of reform and development, state-owned enterprises, especially central enterprises, are mostly in important industries and fields in China's economy, and their overall profitability is strong and relatively stable.
Among them, the leading enterprises continue to achieve better and stronger.
On July 10, the executive meeting of the State Council decided to comprehensively promote the transfer of some state-owned capital to enrich the work of the Social Security Fund this year.
The Ministry of Finance immediately said that it will work with relevant departments, according to the deployment of the executive meeting of the State Council, to comprehensively promote the transfer of some state-owned capital to enrich the social security fund, fully reflecting the intergenerational fairness of the basic pension insurance system and the sharing of the development results of state-owned enterprises.
The second step of the transfer, "addition results", is to enhance the sustainability of China's social security fund, to further consolidate the foundation of the pension social security system.
With the aging of the population, China's social security funds are under pressure, and most of the state-owned capital, which is the main subject of the transfer, has the ability to continue to make profits and dividends, which can not only effectively supplement the social security fund, but also provide the source of living water for the social security fund.
It is estimated that each transfer of 3.8 percentage points of state-owned capital can support the proportion of basic pension insurance in enterprises by 1 percentage point.
The third step of the transfer, "adding results", is to add stabilizers to the capital market.
The transfer of the main body to obtain income is "dividend-based, operating as a supplement".
The social security fund, as a financial investor of state-owned capital, does obtain equity dividend income.
However, as a value investor in the capital market, the social security fund has a strong capital operation ability.
For listed assets in state-owned capital, the participation of the Social Security Fund in shareholding will further optimize the governance structure of listed corporate legal persons, which is conducive to improving the level of enterprise operation and has a positive impact on listed companies and the capital market.
At the same time, the social security fund as an investment vane, the increase in the weight of shareholding is conducive to further enhancing its influence in the market, and play a "stabilizer" role in the market.
In addition, it is also conducive to giving full play to the "value discovery" function of institutional investors, and guiding investors to invest rationally and value.
