According to the relevant person in charge of the project department of Tianjin Zhoutaofu Financial Center of the Eighth Bureau of China Construction, the total amount of steel used in the project exceeds 70,000 tons, the high-altitude group is about 376,000 meters of welds, which is equivalent to the height of 42.5 Everest peaks, and the use of welded wire can circle the earth 40 times, the number of steel components reaches 42,000, and more than 50% is non-standard components, which includes the double-pipe elliptical section column with a single-layer distortion angle of 90 degrees.
The complexity and processing difficulty of the steel structure of the Tianjin Zhoutaofu project is unprecedented.
Industry insiders said that Tianjin Zhou Taifu Financial Center, in the skyscraper project that has been built or built in the country, took the lead in implementing the management of building information modeling (BIM) in an all-round way.
Creatively proposed and successfully implemented the "three full BIM applications" model of full participation, full professional application, and whole process implementation, and developed a collaborative management platform based on high-precision BIM models.
The person in charge said that in the construction process of Zhou Taifu, the project department first carried out BIM construction in the virtual world, and then carried out the physical construction after scientific and correct verification, thus eliminating the problems that may have been demolished and reworked in the previous construction project.
In 2017, the BIM innovation achievements of the Chow Tai Fook Financial Center project won the first prize of the global engineering construction industry global excellence award construction team at the global AU Master Hui and the 2017 Global Engineering Construction Industry Global Excellence Award Ceremony.
During the construction of the project, the project department created more than 130 national patent achievements.
It is worth mentioning that the Tianjin Zhou Taifu Project BIM innovation achievements and scientific and technological innovation promotion, not only make the complex, a large number of construction links all achieved an excellent, construction period shortened by more than four months, but also led to a substantial improvement in safety management and other aspects.
